## Update a Dynamic Spotlight Ad Creative

\*   [http](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/linkedin/marketing/integrations/ads/advertising-targeting/version/spotlight-ads?view=li-lms-2022-08&tabs=http#tabpanel_3_http)
\*   [curl](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/linkedin/marketing/integrations/ads/advertising-targeting/version/spotlight-ads?view=li-lms-2022-08&tabs=http#tabpanel_3_curl)


HTTPCopy

```
POST https://api.linkedin.com/rest/creatives/{sponsoredCreative-urn}

```

JSONCopy

```
{
    "patch": {
        "$set": {
            "content": {
                "spotlight": {
                    "callToAction": "New Action",
                    "description": "New Description",
                    "headline": "New Headline",
                    "landingPage": "http://example.com",                       
                    "organizationName": "New Organization Name",
                    "logo": "urn:li:image:def",
                    "showMemberProfilePhoto": false
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

```

A successful response returns a `204 No Content`.

Makes a BATCH_GET request to let a list of conversations that are created.

